                  "name": "p2",
                  "fill": "#1E2935",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": 358,
                  "content": "A lightweight, Machine Learning-augmented probabilistic correction layer that snaps into existing physics-based propagators to provide statistically calibrated uncertainty.",
